        "content": "<p>The theorem <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=List.Pairwise.forall#doc\">docs#List.Pairwise.forall</a> assumes <code>a ≠ b</code>, but it should still be true with this assumption on a reflexive relation.</p>",
